Package de.unihd.dbs.uima.annotator.heideltime.utilities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ContextAnalyzer
    This class contains methods that work with the dependence of a subject with its surrounding data; namely via the jcas element or a subset list.
    DateCalculator
    This class contains methods that rely on calendar functions to calculate data.
    Logger
    Logger class to facilitate a centralized logging effort.
    Toolbox
    The Toolbox class contains methods with functionality that you would also find outside the context of HeidelTime's specific skillset; i.e. they do not require the CAS context, but are 'useful code snippets'.
